{"tid":1914824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［完整］2020立法會泛民有意參選名單","createTime":"2020-03-07T19:32:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T05:30:50.000Z","uid":129134,"like":29,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"55815d9cf9a31ddba1ae069ec89d515a3fe1257d","tid":1914824,"uid":129134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T19:32:30.000Z","msg":"<strong>港島</strong><br />\n（應協調3-4席）<br />\n許智峯 <br />\n黎明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鄭達鴻<br />\n羅冠聰<br />\n楊雪盈<br />\n<br />\n<strong>新東</strong><br />\n（應協調6-7席）<br />\n楊岳橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陳志全<br />\n立場姐姐<br />\n林卓廷<br />\n柯耀林/區鎮樺<br />\n張超雄/郭永健<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咖哩飯<br />\n劉穎匡<br />\n長毛<br />\n<br />\n<strong>新西</strong><br />\n（應協調5-6席）<br />\n朱凱迪<br />\n尹兆堅<br />\n郭家麒<br />\n巫堃泰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n白頭佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n王伯羽<br />\n天水圍<br />\n鄭松泰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n譚凱邦<br />\n吳敏兒/趙恩來<br />\n<br />\n<strong>九西</strong><br />\n（應協調4席）<br />\n毛姨<br />\n黃碧雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/袁海文 <br />\n鄺葆賢<br />\n余德寶<br />\n張崑陽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n李傲然<br />\n黃毓民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n岑敖暉<br />\n劉小麗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n曾健超<br />\n何啟明<br />\n施安娜<br />\n潘焯鴻<br />\n又一村大狀<br />\n<br />\n<strong>九東</strong><br />\n（應協調3席）<br />\n莫嘉嫻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n譚文豪<br />\n黃之鋒/梁凱晴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快必<br />\n譚香文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>區一（送位）</strong><br />\n（應協調1席）<br />\n李嘉偉<br />\n王進洋<br />\n黃國桐<br />\n趙家賢<br />\n張文龍<br />\n劉卓裕<br />\n機場大叔<br />\n<br />\n<strong>區二（超區）</strong><br />\n（應協調3席）<br />\n鄺俊宇<br />\n涂謹申<br />\n岑子杰<br />\n黃文萱<br />\n張秀賢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n柯耀林/區鎮樺<br />\n<br />\n資料來自：蘋果、01、綜合連登<br />\n*SORRY我本土，好憎幫藍絲新移民嘅人，雖然我心底覺得有必要搵人拎新移民票<br />\n<br />\n以下純個人意見<br />\n1、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">必須要協調，不肯協調者絕對不投</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2、有時唔係話要求素人有咩政績，而係最低限度都要有知名度、有做過一啲嘢比人睇到，例如上屆朱凱迪羅冠聰甚至梁天琦呢種都係搞運動出身，或者有新的思潮帶出嚟，大家會有信心。而那些反送中臨尾先出嚟選區選，都仲未做好現有的工作，又唔係有個好強的政治理念，又唔係在反送中入面有好明顯的投入，而家見勢好又出嚟選立會，其實同機會主義者有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n3、好心班老一輩泛民快少少交棒，白頭佬、一舊雲上屆咩政績有目共睹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 九東民主黨交棒點知原來交比個近50歲的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 劉小麗仲想繼續玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 長毛老喇好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4、如果盡數贏：港島取4、新東取7、新西取6、九西取4、九東取3、區一取1、區二取3，共28席<br />\n<br />\n功能組別現時贏：教育、法律、會計、醫學、衛生、社福、IT，共7席<br />\n有機會爆冷贏：工程、測量、藝文、零售、飲食<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">加埋35席就可以停擺立法會，停止對警犬一切撥款</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未登記做選民快少少登記<br />\n飲食及零售老闆、工程師快少少登記做功能組別<br />\n呢場仗贏唔到，對唔住坐監及死去手足"},{"pid":"04d91e8f33f3fdf38b26784f4d057d59f29582b6","tid":1914824,"uid":323113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T19:55:26.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"83f5e8405b25b27c70592207021456d48c3a5337","tid":1914824,"uid":129134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:03:43.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"024be67e6b9dfee319ad7d122d24a5a3212cfb8d","tid":1914824,"uid":129134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:04:58.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"3181f7a95064c84b47af3b165afd0f7bb9af914e","tid":1914824,"uid":94502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:09:01.000Z","msg":"九東黃洋達同東九都唔出咩"},{"pid":"456e2d956f062e72d1a2c489b2ac0e8363a1ab31","tid":1914824,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:16:07.000Z","msg":"岑傲暉好似代表「朱迪+眾志」聯盟選超區？<br />\n「朱迪+眾志」聯盟派張崑陽選九西<br />\n岑子杰反而可能選新東接長毛個位"},{"pid":"a1ff72a35db246ff0fdbf5ffa291ebe2140f057d","tid":1914824,"uid":101392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:18:28.000Z","msg":"另外潘焯鴻雖然好值得尊重<br />\n但係佢係「田少+薯片」聯盟<br />\n屬於開明建制派 唔該唔好擺落個list度"},{"pid":"40c0820470adff89603e89ca2b0625b9c8587cef","tid":1914824,"uid":144883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:21:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />楊岳橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />張超雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />梁耀忠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黃碧雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe0784cd3825b8957869b6d6ef5260ca62de5ae","tid":1914824,"uid":129134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a1ff72a35db246ff0fdbf5ffa291ebe2140f057d","tid":1914824,"uid":101392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:18:28.000Z","msg":"另外潘焯鴻雖然好值得尊重<br />\n但係佢係「田少+薯片」聯盟<br />\n屬於開明建制派 唔該唔好擺落個list度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:23:04.000Z","msg":"你岩 佢應該要拎藍絲飛"},{"pid":"d3ba49e89064aa68b771f36bbfe5dd8a470a408d","tid":1914824,"uid":227312,"