"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n岑敖暉<br />\n劉小麗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n曾健超<br />\n何啟明<br />\n施安娜<br />\n潘焯鴻<br />\n又一村大狀<br />\n<br />\n九東<br />\n（應協調3席）<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">莫嘉嫻</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">譚文豪</span><br />\n黃之鋒/<span style=\"color: blue;\">梁凱晴</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快必<br />\n譚香文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n區一（送位）<br />\n（應協調1席）<br />\n李嘉偉<br />\n王進洋<br />\n黃國桐<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">趙家賢</span><br />\n張文龍<br />\n劉卓裕<br />\n機場大叔<br />\n<br />\n區二（超區）<br />\n（應協調3席）<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">鄺俊宇</span><br />\n涂謹申<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">岑子杰</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">黃文萱</span><br />\n張秀賢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n柯耀林/區鎮樺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T04:34:51.000Z","msg":"張超雄宣布不角逐連任立法會<br />\n<br />\n連同今屆立法會，工黨張超雄已擔任三屆立法會議員，他接受《香港01》查詢時承認，下屆不會再參選，很大機會由工黨主席郭永健接棒，又指他下屆有可能排名第二參選，為郭永健「抬橋」。<br />\n<br />\n張超雄表示，他從政以來已三次成功當選立法會議員，認為能擔此重任是十分榮幸和保貴，不過他表示下屆將不會排首位參選，認為是時候換個崗位，「長江後浪推前浪，應給多些機會後生仔」。"},{"pid":"b863daf283a5bc2ece061184b65d9be6cd9f86ed","tid":1914824,"uid":218082,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T04:35:39.000Z","msg":"黃毓民話參選擺明9up都計埋落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83aab7213be9bd20b1ad9a81525d3935219df706","tid":1914824,"uid":281401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:00:31.000Z","msg":"點解尋晚香港「水晶之夜」一定係國際線大講特講<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/